  "decision_conditions": [
    "•\tReason:  The proposed erection of a full mansard roof extension by reason of its inappropriate design, scale and massing would fail to bear any relationship to its surrounding context. The development would result in an overdominant and discordant feature when viewed from the streetscene surrounding Mountgrove Road. The proposed development is therefore considered to have a detrimental impact on the existing character and appearance of the area. The development is therefore considered contrary to Islington's Unitary Development Plan policies D1 (Design), D4 (Design in context), D11 (Alterations and extensions) and Islington’s Urban Design Guidance 2006."
